  "claim_short": "Let \\(G:X\\to Y\\) be a norm-one finite-rank operator with the alternative Daugavet property. Then \\[ B_X=\\overline{\\operatorname{conv}}\\{x\\in S_X:\\|Gx\\|=1\\}. \\] In particular, \\(G\\) attains its norm. Consequently every finite-rank spear operator attains its norm.",
